This paper focuses on natural language understanding and commonsense reasoning, which are core topics in the field of natural language processing (NLP) and artificial intelligence (AI). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category for this paper. Additionally, the paper discusses learning and inference approaches, which are also relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper may also touch on computer vision (cs.CV) as some commonsense knowledge is visual in nature. Finally, the paper may also be relevant to other sub-categories such as cs.CC (Computational Complexity) and cs.SE (Software Engineering) as it discusses the limitations and challenges of current approaches.
